    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Remix does not support function type parameters yet. Remix is using `ethers.js` to encode and decode parameters. So if `ethers.js` does not support function type parameters, remix can't either. I'v already submitted an issue, check this -- #3887\r\n\r\nAnd I submitted a [PR](https://github.com/ethers-io/ethers.js/pull/4217) in `ethers.js`, but it's still not merged.",
